rule-16-2-a.test_description: A building with an elevator has matching motor schedules between the baseline and proposed ruleset model descriptions.

standard.rule_description: The baseline elevator motor use shall be modeled with the same schedule as the proposed design.

rule-16-2-b.test_description: A building with an elevator has motor schedules which do not match between the baseline and proposed ruleset model descriptions.

standard.rule_description: The baseline elevator motor use shall be modeled with the same schedule as the proposed design.

rule-16-2-c.test_description: A baseline building has an elevator with schedules but has no proposed elevator equivalent. Expected result: NOT APPLICABLE

standard.rule_description: The baseline elevator motor use shall be modeled with the same schedule as the proposed design.

rule-16-2-d.test_description: A building with an elevator has the proposed elevator cab ventilation fan modeled with the same schedule as the proposed elevator motor.

standard.rule_description: The baseline elevator motor use shall be modeled with the same schedule as the proposed design.
